NAME
    Ballerina new - Create a Ballerina project

SYNOPSIS
    ballerina new <project-name>

DESCRIPTION
     Ballerina new command creates a new directory and initialize a
     Ballerina project inside it.

     The created set of artifacts includes a Ballerina.toml and Ballerina
     project directory structure. You can use Ballerina.toml to manage
     the organization setting and version for the project.

     Ballerina project is identified by the Ballerina.toml file. Ballerina
     modules should be placed under src directory. 

EXAMPLES
     Create a new project 
     $ ballerina new my-project

